now though i can't wait to find out =). <br><br>for me, i really enjoy pulling and i think that despite the relative frailty of SK's compared to warriors, SK's past 30 are better pullers for no reason other than feign death. it's nice to be able to cancel a pull without dieing.<br><br>btw - i'm fairly poor in the grand scheme of things and have been lucky enough to have been gifted nice slashing weapons - dark reaver / sporali defender.<br><br>what would you recommend for 1h blunt / piercing. i'm currently using velium which is ok, but no great shakes as they say?<br><br>Colinmarsh<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
