	   <tr><td colspan=2>Actually, you are absolutely correct, I didnt mention criticals that WAR get.&nbsp;&nbsp;That is definitely an advantage.  But I also didnt mention certain self-buffs that SKs get that can proc &amp; do additional damage / heal the SK.  Granted, i think that the crit prob does more overall damage, but it is similar to the proc...it doesnt happen consistently.<br><br>As far as pulling with a pet....oh yes...VERY challenging to do without him screwing it all up      heh<br><br>Im not gonna say that a SK will outdamage a WAR post 50, just that I think that SKs can at least come close, if not surpass them.  This is nothing more than my opinion, as I have not done any statistical analysis, but I honestly believe it.<br><br>As far as weapons go, I am far more versed in 1HB than piercing weapons, probably due to the fact that my experience has been that a good 1HB weapon is far easier to get than a good piercing weapon.  I am familiar with several good piercing weapons &amp; can tell you what I think of them, but 1HB seems the better/easier route to go to me, but I form no conclusions on that.  Personally, I love MoSS until you can upgrade to Ebon Mace.  Both are fairly common on the server that I play on &amp; MoSS is dirt cheap (cheaper than a Wurm &amp; has a better dmg per sec).  The drawback of both, however, is that they are fairly fast &amp; you can easily be waiting to swing while casting a spell.  Hence, a long delay, high damage 2HS sometimes makes sense, but whatever you prefer, go for it    =)<br><br>Lunatic<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
